<h2>Before you start</h2>

<em><strong>Please read carefully!!</strong></em>

<strong>Requirements</strong>
<p>
	Code-Gallery have some fondamental requirements:
	<ul>
		<li>Python 2.4 or higher</li>
		<li>ImageMagick 6 or higher</li>
	</ul>
	And if you want to use the GUI the extra requirements are:
	<ul>
		<li>GTK+ 2.6 or higher</li>
		<li>PyGTK 2.6 or hogher</li>
		<li>libglade 2 or higher</li>
	</ul>
</p>